sql:
SELECT location, registration, address
FROM precincts
WHERE registration = (SELECT MAX(registration) FROM precincts);

SELECT precinct_id, ballot_type, SUM(count) AS total_ballots_cast, MAX(timestamp) AS last_cast_timestamp
FROM ballot_cast
GROUP BY precinct_id, ballot_type;

external_knowledge:
No external knowledge is required to answer this question; 
Election details include the election ID, type, and date; 
Election type could be general, primary, or other; 
Voting precincts refer to designated areas where voters cast their ballots.

sql:
SELECT precinct_id, SUM(votes) AS total_votes
FROM voting_results
GROUP BY precinct_id;
